Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.40,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What was that back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:09.94,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hasumi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.81,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I'm actually going to Germany next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:14.98,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I wish you two happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:17.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It's not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.50,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:24.69,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,let's have a good time for the remaining week...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:27.16,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.96,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.41,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I better make that omelette rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:50.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're just trying to trouble me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,By teasing me, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:53.92,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Were you able to fool Hasumi-kun all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:58.65,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Really? Then I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.33,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, didn't you say that you'd always stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:06.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Always and forever, until I became a grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.36,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,There's no way we could do that, realistically speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It's wrong to keep doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:13.10,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,That's what you said yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:19.14,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't know, but we were probably both thinking that deep inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.31,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,that this would end someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:23.04,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Am I wrong? {orig: Aren't I right?}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:34.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You can't just decide on you own like that, with just a week left!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:38.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Well, to be specific, more like six days and two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:42.10,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,But then Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.40,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I think I should leave here around Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.77,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I have to go home and get my luggage together.{pack my bags.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're seriously serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.64,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,That's what I've been saying this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:55.24,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It was a pretty prestigious competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.75,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Although I did have the confidence to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Until when?{How long?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.08,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,About three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:07.16,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I think it's about time I went back to being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:28.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.25,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:38.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know what to say after you suddenly pop that kind of news to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Don't make a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.26,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You're selfish, aren't you, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Even though you'll forget about me within a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.63,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Even though you're going to forget about me and be sleeping here with Hasumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:59.57,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,So you don't have to make a face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.51,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Why don't you just leave me alone? I'm just a pet anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:07.82,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,If you're lonely, there are a lot of dogs and cats and guys around that could fill my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.35,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,They'll obediently stay at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.72,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,and you can pet them or play with them whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you saying?! Do you seriously mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.06,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You know yourself that you're not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:18.73,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.67,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.54,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What am I to you, Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I understand, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Let's just enjoy the rest of our short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.77,title,text,0,0,0,,Kimi wa petto
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.77,episode,text,0,0,0,,Story 9: On the last night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.00,Text_1,text,0,0,0,,Three more days
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,This is the data I told you about pertaining to the EU member nations' summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.41,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.75,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's really helpful to have it organised like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:30.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,This place has gotten a little less popular with the introduction of the online database, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:36.03,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I like this place.\NI can randomly search through data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.00,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}What kind of relationship are you two in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.44,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:49.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that moment, if I had told him the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:54.12,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what senpai would have thought of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.75,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,There you go, looking troubled again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.13,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, when you were giving that bouquet of flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.36,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,you seemed like a totally different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.63,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really, with him, we're just childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.20,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I know. I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.78,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Well, I'll call you tonight then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.93,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I wonder why I'm questioning her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.30,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,There you are, Goto-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.67,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Can you hand this over to your chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.07,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,All right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.24,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.07,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:56.01,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,{\i1}I like you, Hasumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.55,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san, phone call for you on line 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.45,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:14.30,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Feel each other's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:16.97,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Yes, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.30,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.44,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.78,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.28,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I'm doing very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.58,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.01,Petto_basic_2,Junpei,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you two saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:36.38,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, Takeshi! You can speak German!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:39.69,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I've been there a few times when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.69,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.26,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.70,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.29,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Don't come with me, I'm going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.90,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Then what do you mean? Did you break up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.13,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Nope. I told her I'd leave first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.87,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Because if she threw me away, I would've felt like dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.11,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.72,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.56,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What happened with your dog, Momo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.23,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It seems he's going to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.80,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What... Frankfurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:21.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.13,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He won a prestigious competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.43,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:31.11,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm surprised. I didn't know you were such a brilliant top breeder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, it's just that he was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:39.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,The grace period has ended. If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.22,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Could it be that Iwaya-san's Momo-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.62,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may be soft, but I am not a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:52.26,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}But to desire something that you lack,\NI think it's okay to call that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:57.07,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Perhaps a boy with a gentle smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.00,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Heh, a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:18.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}But don't you think one person and a pet is a lot better than just one person alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.42,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I have to see him off properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.82,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,I can't believe she'd throw Takeshi away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:57.99,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Takeshi's always been admired by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:02.20,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,But I'm glad he decided to go abroad. You have so much talent, after all.{"You"? don't you mean "he"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Look, look. You were in the evening paper. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.78,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Wow, I'm already in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's so amazing, when you're dancing, you seem like a totally different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't call you Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Goda Takeshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,This reporter was saying it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.22,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That it must be such an honor for me\Nto be a childhood friend of Goda Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He wanted so badly to do a report on you that he brought senpai with him to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.40,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.17,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He said he's never seen such a high grand jet. He was really impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.97,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's so cool-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:42.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,So strong and beautiful. It even made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:47.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I guess it's odd for me to be bragging about it, when I have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's so awesome. It's almost absurd that someone like you stays here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.22,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,So I'll cheer for you from now on too—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.22,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.52,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What's that? It pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean, it pisses you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I wasn't like that at all, was I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:09.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What... what are you saying all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.83,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Calling me Takeshi-san and stuff?\NYou know me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.77,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I was such an awful bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.71,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I can't do anything, I'm stupid, and I fail easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Totally irresponsible and useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.51,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,That's what you said yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.88,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You know me! Didn't you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.15,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Then why do you say things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.02,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What I mean is, I don't want to hear words like that come from your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Why do you say that you have nothing to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.39,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You said I was useless but that you still needed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.86,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I thought that you alone understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:47.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sorry. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.14,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Whatever kind of Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wherever you go, Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:46.09,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll always love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:59.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I realised that the reason Momo was here was the same reason why I wanted him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:05.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}A place where we could be our true selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:11.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone who would unconditionally accept who we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a little while,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll lose it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.30,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.94,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I think I'm starting to feel a bit of lust...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.00,Text_1,text,0,0,0,,Two more days
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.35,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.00,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Let me come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.85,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Forgive me! I regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.48,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,How can I forgive such a horny male dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.42,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,But it's a natural phenomenon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:19.05,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I wasn't thinking of anything perverted, but my body just did it on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:19.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,All lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.09,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's not a lie! My lower body, on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Enough! I don't want to hear any more of such a detailed excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.40,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you so angry about it? I'm being so honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean, why? It was a bit of a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was caring for you as such a cute pet, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.38,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It's not like you're the mother of a son who's going through puberty
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:38.11,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,and found pornographic magazines in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think it's close to that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.94,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm not stuck here for the rest of the time, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Punished for the rest of the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:49.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yup, I'm not so soft a master as to exempt you from punishment just because there are only two days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:52.99,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Wait, wait a sec. Like this? Really like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.69,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, tonight I may be just a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.89,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Wait, hey! Wait a— Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:10.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Damn. I wonder how many years it's been since I've cried in front of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.26,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san, the organisation from Kansai asked for you to call them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.36,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Higuchi-kun, can you give this to the revision board?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:35.96,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:38.07,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san, could you look over this for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,With this, I don't think there's anything wrong with the structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I think the revision board will check this notation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Consult the stylebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:45.67,Petto_basic_2,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.50,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san, there's a phone call from the Visual department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.65,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.45,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Iwaya, I think we're going to go with this for the next cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.45,note,text,0,0,0,,The interaction between a pet and a human
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Pets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.25,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Yeah. I remember you owning a dog or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:55.60,note,text,0,0,0,,Pet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:56.90,note,text,0,0,0,,Stressful society
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.30,note,text,0,0,0,,Healing power
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.35,note,text,0,0,0,,Pet and human
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.09,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,That's really low of you, to make a young man a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.93,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,...won't last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.73,Petto_basic_2,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Which are you going to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:04.59,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.86,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.44,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I apologise. I'm the one at fault. I understand that well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:25.51,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll return your call later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:29.05,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Are... Are you all right? Get... get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:33.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh... I... I'm sorry. Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:36.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. It's just that all of a sudden, things just started spinning inside my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.20,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.20,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,But that was so unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:43.37,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.63,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,It happens to me sometimes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.90,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,In the middle of the night, when I have night duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:50.37,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, I get this urge to yell something like, "Stupid idiot!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.47,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.96,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,There was one time that I went to the snack room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.48,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,and took all the paper cups out of the drawer and put teeth marks on all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.68,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,Are you serious? That's gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.65,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,I also threw my shoes at the boss's desk once in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.42,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Hey, hey... why am I always the bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:07.56,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,I got it! I'll take you all out to eat as my treat sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.42,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Are you for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.03,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Sure, the women too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.53,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Don't say you won't stick around after 5 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:13.80,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,All right, it's nice once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.36,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's okay that I can go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.07,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.60,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,And we all want to hear the truth behind all those rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:26.27,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Plus, you don't seek any advice from your primary supervisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.22,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:42.26,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,It's no big deal. We're all coworkers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:57.64,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,No. I don't want to go if it's not Maldives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.28,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,But I don't want it to seem too much like a newlyweds thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.00,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,That's what's so great about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.00,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,How about Hakone, like last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.98,Petto_basic_2,Kuraki,0,0,0,,No! We went there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.82,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:08.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.49,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Have we been found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.22,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.03,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,We got engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:16.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.76,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,It's surprising, isn't it? I'm sure you're surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.66,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.76,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a surprise for me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.43,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Oh, you have to come to our wedding too, Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.10,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Oh, but by that time, she may already be in Rio de Janeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh... I don't plan on going to Rio de Janeiro yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.61,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,You're kidding, you're not going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.95,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Why? Why aren't you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:41.22,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,Hey, you shouldn't go digging into people's business like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.82,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:46.55,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Aww, Nobu-chan, you're too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.19,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't even know why myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.06,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I so tangled up and immobile?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:58.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have the courage to get married nor to go to Rio de Janeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not even the courage to ask Momo to stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm just a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.86,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're going to turn down the marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to ask him to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're running away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's just for now. Just for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:32.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm finally getting used to work, and I like my job, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:36.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's really hard, but I'll just have to continue it long distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of mustering up the guts to tell senpai that tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.68,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Why don't you at least get the marriage certificate, and have a separated life for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.00,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Or maybe you can just have an engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But I don't like to leave things half-done like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:51.99,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,But long distance, without any promises?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.79,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,It's on the other side of the world, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:55.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:04.30,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,That kind of place is an extremely long distance away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yup. The direct flights there are only four times a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,At the shortest, it takes twenty-five hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:12.37,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,The time difference is twelve hours. If I make phone calls in the morning, it'll be the best time for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.44,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You can make calculations like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:15.78,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,And Momo is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.22,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,That's pretty far too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.70,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:41.14,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You really don't have any self-awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.94,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.07,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Why do you seem sadder about your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:53.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's not true, but he's leaving soon, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.62,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:58.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.96,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's only a pet, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.10,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Within this month, I plan on leaving this apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.70,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.70,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.47,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Due to business-related matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:25.35,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Shimizu-san, you were a very good resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:30.59,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,You were very good about disposing of your trash and in terms of your daily practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:31.75,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:37.73,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Then let's do this. Why don't we swap email addresses?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.70,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:44.93,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Then how about on this dustpan, in permanent marker?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:47.04,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Where's that permanent marker...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:47.60,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:51.64,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Hey, it's you! Your dancing was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.38,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, you came to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:54.31,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:22:00.40,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,But I'm sorry. I don't remember which floor you reside on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.98,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, that's because I wasn't a resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.59,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I was a pet, owned on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:09.92,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,A pet? Could it be Iwaya-san's?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:10.29,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:14.20,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes, but this doesn't mean that Takeshi-san lives off women's money or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.13,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,By next week, he's going to be studying abroad at a dance school in Frankfurt, Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:18.13,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:19.13,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:24.81,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Time to say goodbye to this apartment too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:37.49,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:42.32,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,If you're looking for Sumire-chan, I think she's at Hasumi-kun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:43.59,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:46.63,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you to forget about what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:50.50,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,So you're giving up on Hasumi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.27,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'm just changing my plan of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:55.70,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:02.11,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hey, do you think if I took Hasumi-san away, that woman would come and take him back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:09.42,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Hmm, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:12.32,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I think too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:17.03,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,But then, what does that mean?\NDoesn't it mean she doesn't truly like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:22.36,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I think she does like him, like a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:29.04,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But you know, she probably doesn't want to get all resentful, or show her true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:34.68,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Meaning she's just a jumble of complexes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:42.70,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hmm, when she has those great looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:48.92,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,If I had those brains and that face and body, I would take advantage of them a million times better.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:53.70,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But well, because she's that kind of a person, you want to be near her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:57.77,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Because even if you ran away, she wouldn't come chasing after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:23:59.47,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You want her to come after you, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:02.17,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I did want her to come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:04.84,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Although I knew it was too much to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:08.28,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You're spoiling your master too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:12.68,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Why do you think there's an increasing number of women who can only love their pets?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.65,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,These are mostly women with careers and high educational backgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:17.55,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:23.89,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,they always have their armor around their hearts in order to stand up to the pressures of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:25.80,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,So there is a larger gap. In private,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.80,0:24:30.57,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,they want to take that armor off and have someone towards whom they can be unconditionally gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:33.30,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,But they can't take their armor off in front of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.54,0:24:38.24,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,That's why they love their pets too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:39.77,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,An armor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.47,0:24:42.38,Petto_basic_2,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, a heavy, super-hard armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.84,0:24:44.99,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You know, with those elite, highly educated women.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.99,0:24:50.79,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,they have this aura that screams, "Don't touch me!" It's so impudent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.79,0:24:53.59,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,That's why, honestly, men back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:57.99,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,"Oh, really? Then go live your lives however you want to!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.99,0:24:59.66,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,That's how they respond to women like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:03.83,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll live my life as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.70,0:25:05.83,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,What, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.83,0:25:08.77,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,It seems that I am a disciple of Iwaya-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.14,0:25:13.61,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,But on your resume you wrote...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.61,0:25:17.61,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I lied. I'm currently in my fourth year at the Literature department of Tokyo University.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.61,0:25:23.59,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Because you wouldn't have hired me if I was a smart woman, would you, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.92,0:25:27.66,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:34.50,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you've never stayed over at my place before, have you, Iwaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.96,0:25:38.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.07,0:25:44.21,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Last time you came over, you rushed home saying you had to feed your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.04,0:25:51.91,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hey, what was it that you wanted to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.78,0:25:58.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh... it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.62,0:26:00.46,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not that big of a deal anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.60,0:26:10.97,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Actually, today... my boss called me to his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.90,0:26:14.94,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's been decided that I have to return to Rio de Janeiro next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.24,0:26:22.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is that... so?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.31,0:26:28.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's been decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.56,0:26:39.86,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Won't you stay over tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.10,0:26:41.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.63,0:26:43.37,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.37,0:26:50.74,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You make me feel uneasy.\NYou've never once worn that ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.04,0:26:54.78,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, that's because I didn't want to get any scratches on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.78,0:26:58.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,And I didn't want the people back at work saying things either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.35,0:27:00.82,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm... it's not that I don't want to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.82,0:27:05.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's just that there's my job, and I just haven't been able to sort out my feelings yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.79,0:27:07.96,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Is that really the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.89,0:27:17.43,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Honestly, I have no idea what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.14,0:27:23.41,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,At least in front of me, I want you to show me your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.68,0:27:29.41,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,My true self?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.21,0:27:32.91,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,The true Iwaya, as she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.49,0:27:39.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What is "as I am" anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.79,0:27:42.66,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What kind of face should I show?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.92,0:27:45.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What kind of person am I in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.03,0:27:49.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.66,0:27:54.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I just wanted to be liked by you,\Nto become the person you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.10,0:27:56.57,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can't even thrust my feelings at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.57,0:27:59.57,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't even know what part of me you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.57,0:28:02.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not so easy to show who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.78,0:28:07.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,The real me...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.82,0:28:10.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,is a lot worse than what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.02,0:28:16.89,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,The worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.26,0:28:21.19,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.00,0:28:21.70,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.00,0:28:28.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That boy whom I gave the flower bouquet is not my childhood friend at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.11,0:28:32.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.68,0:28:39.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.38,0:28:46.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I kept him at my home as a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.35,0:28:47.42,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.23,0:28:54.16,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.66,0:28:56.53,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.53,0:28:58.93,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I just didn't want you to misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.27,0:29:02.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,There is nothing between me and that boy, just a good relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.74,0:29:04.91,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,A good relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.51,0:29:08.24,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Are you seriously saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.62,0:29:20.29,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.56,0:29:22.92,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Can I ask you to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.16,0:29:26.26,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.10,0:29:29.90,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I need some time to think alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:36.74,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Can you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.61,0:29:41.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.92,0:29:51.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.02,0:29:52.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm myself down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.90,0:30:03.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, Sumire-chan. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.03,0:30:05.00,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.57,0:30:06.23,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.54,0:30:11.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.44,0:30:20.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.79,0:30:30.89,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What did you end up telling him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.63,0:30:34.36,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I lied so many times for your sake and you ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.20,0:30:39.27,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.84,0:30:50.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll cook something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.92,0:30:55.48,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't mind staying like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.05,0:31:00.52,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I don't mind if we just stay like this for the next two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.36,0:31:06.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Because you can only cry in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.60,0:31:20.11,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}People need someone with whom they can be truly selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.24,0:31:23.45,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.61,0:31:28.62,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the reason I was tied down here all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.30,0:31:59.30,Text_1,text,0,0,0,,One more day
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.45,0:32:04.62,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Iwaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.62,0:32:07.09,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,It seems she's taken today and tomorrow off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.66,0:32:10.23,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,I suppose she must really not have been feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.13,0:32:13.03,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.03,0:32:13.70,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.70,0:32:15.03,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.80,0:32:17.00,note,text,0,0,0,,Request for resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.07,0:32:17.77,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.77,0:32:19.90,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Please take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.67,0:32:26.98,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,All right. It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.48,0:32:31.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Tada! Meal requests for today and tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:35.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Aren't there a lot of carbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.15,0:32:36.79,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.29,0:32:39.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'll make them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.69,0:32:40.79,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Score!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.73,0:32:44.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.16,0:32:46.96,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,This is your schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.20,0:32:48.33,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You made something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.33,0:32:50.77,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll come pick you up tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.77,0:32:52.97,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Please get your baggage together by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.57,0:32:53.74,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,No, I don't need anyone to pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.74,0:32:55.37,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I can go home on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.37,0:32:57.87,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,No, it would be awful if you got into an accident on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.87,0:32:58.54,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.54,0:33:01.28,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,No, you're actually pretty spaced out at time, so it's a necessary precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.28,0:33:04.71,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,And we will take you straight back to your home in Chiba, and we will finish packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.71,0:33:06.92,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,and three days later, on June 14th, 13:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.92,0:33:09.72,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,your plane is scheduled to leave from Narita Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.82,0:33:09.85,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.95,0:33:10.99,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.99,0:33:12.85,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You should take up ballet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.19,0:33:17.13,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I think you'd be better suited for it than doing stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.56,0:33:20.66,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll give it a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.66,0:33:21.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.06,0:33:24.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Shall I prepare some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.87,0:33:28.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Who is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.90,0:33:31.37,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,My, my... Shimizu-san, you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.37,0:33:32.44,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes, I got here before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.44,0:33:37.41,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Takeshi-kun, here's a globe for you. I think it'll be useful when you get over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.41,0:33:38.41,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.88,0:33:41.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then maybe we should all have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.85,0:33:43.85,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Who now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.22,0:33:46.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,What?! How come there are so many people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.49,0:33:47.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.02,0:33:49.52,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.52,0:33:51.69,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,My, long time no see, my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.86,0:33:52.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,How about you, Yuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.99,0:33:54.00,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,What, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.46,0:33:57.17,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I just came to see him one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.80,0:34:00.87,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I guess things are more cheerful than I expected things to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.94,0:34:02.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yuri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.87,0:34:05.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You know, Hasumi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.24,0:34:08.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I told him the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:10.05,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.31,0:34:12.98,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Do you mean about that pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.50,0:34:14.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.89,0:34:19.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.49,0:34:20.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you knew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.79,0:34:24.09,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't be able to hide that pet from him for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.33,0:34:25.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.03,0:34:29.86,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,He was such an important existence for you that you were unable to hide him any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.17,0:34:32.32,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hasumi-san himself knew in the back of his mind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.32,0:34:34.24,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,that there was a secret you were keeping from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.67,0:34:38.97,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,For a while, I thought you might actually choose him instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.87,0:34:40.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.98,0:34:42.18,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.18,0:34:47.48,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Do you know the vow of marriage? It goes, "In sickness and in health..."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.48,0:34:50.62,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,There are not many people you can be with like that in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.99,0:34:55.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Even when you're sick, or healthy, when you're depressed or want to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.49,0:34:56.76,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Even on a deserted island,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.76,0:34:59.79,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,even without makeup on, someone you want to have around wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.83,0:35:02.60,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,That is what's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.73,0:35:08.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But he's going to be gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.21,0:35:16.75,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, I think it's about time we all left.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.75,0:35:20.62,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,But we're still eating... Oh, it's time to do my rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.52,0:35:21.85,Petto_basic_2,Yuri,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.95,0:35:23.92,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,I must hurry along. Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.19,0:35:27.36,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Well, spend the rest of your time together well, just the two of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:28.59,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.06,0:35:30.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Bye, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.11,0:35:46.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Now, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.24,0:35:49.74,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.31,0:35:53.45,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,How about a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.48,0:36:23.48,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Mmm, that feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.22,0:36:29.32,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Ouch, that's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.32,0:36:31.99,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not hot, hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.99,0:36:39.33,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,All right, I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.59,0:36:41.63,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Wow, I feel like I'm in paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.50,0:36:44.87,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,I feel like a prince today.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.67,0:36:50.77,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.17,0:36:51.17,Petto_basic_ending_2,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.51,0:36:53.98,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Hey, this is your comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.04,0:36:56.98,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.31,0:37:00.18,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,You know, I've been thinking this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.18,0:37:06.32,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,That the reality of eternal love is that it's actually just a trade-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.32,0:37:10.79,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,That love is actually something dirty, where you compete with and deceive each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.79,0:37:13.53,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,And you just soak in self-satisfaction by pretending to care for one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.53,0:37:16.90,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,The one who falls in love is the one that loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.90,0:37:17.87,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.87,0:37:22.00,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,It's impossible to unconditionally love a person the way you love a dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.00,0:37:25.91,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,without treatise, not caring about the quality or background of the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.21,0:37:27.21,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.38,0:37:32.01,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,But I think I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.01,0:37:32.75,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.35,0:37:35.65,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, tell Momo-chan that I said hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.18,0:37:38.49,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Tell him that I would've liked to meet him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.89,0:37:45.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Was it someone from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.53,0:37:47.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.83,0:37:49.40,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He said to say hello to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.40,0:37:54.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He's a good person. Always carrying around a Chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.64,0:37:57.44,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,He seems like an interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.74,0:38:02.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,And... what else? Is there anything else you want to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.68,0:38:04.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What else...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.91,0:38:07.28,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,How about a foot massage?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.28,0:38:07.85,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.02,0:38:11.02,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.02,0:38:11.86,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.86,0:38:13.50,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Then I'll do yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.56,0:38:16.12,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, no, you don't have to. I'm ticklish too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.53,0:38:20.46,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.53,0:38:22.33,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.27,0:38:31.41,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.51,0:38:35.71,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,If we don't decide soon, the night will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.21,0:38:41.38,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Then how about telling fun stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.38,0:38:42.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.35,0:38:44.02,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah, stories about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.19,0:38:47.26,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Like, "When was your first love?" and, "When did you lose your virginity?"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.26,0:38:48.09,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.09,0:38:49.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk about such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.56,0:38:51.03,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Then I'll go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.10,0:38:56.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Fine, when was your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.20,0:38:58.57,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.83,0:39:04.67,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,A long time ago, in a certain kingdom, there was a princess who couldn't shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.27,0:39:06.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,A princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.50,0:39:07.50,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.51,0:39:12.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The princess who couldn't shed tears was extremely beautiful, serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.61,0:39:17.89,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,and smart. However, because she wasn't able to express her emotions very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.89,0:39:20.42,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,she was always alone in the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.56,0:39:23.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Could this be about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.83,0:39:26.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Just listen, since the good part is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.06,0:39:32.37,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,And one day, after the princess was dumped by a guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.37,0:39:34.90,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,she found a cardboard box with a dog inside on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.97,0:39:38.74,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The dog was really a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.74,0:39:41.78,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,but because it was so happy to be rescued by the princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.01,0:39:46.21,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,he became a dog and came to live with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.75,0:39:49.12,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,He was actually planning on going home right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.25,0:39:52.69,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,But before he knew it, the dog came to really like the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.29,0:39:57.56,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Why? Because the princess who couldn't shed tears
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.43,0:40:02.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,would shed beautiful tears, only in front of the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.00,0:40:12.57,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,But, right after that, there appeared a handsome prince before the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.51,0:40:20.75,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The dog was slightly shocked, but as long as he stayed a dog, the princess treasured him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.75,0:40:23.69,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,So he decided to continue being a dog for a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.25,0:40:25.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.79,0:40:32.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,One day, the prince finally proposed to the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:37.07,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The dog decided to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.73,0:40:39.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, that's enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.34,0:40:41.97,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The dog thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.67,0:40:50.75,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,"Man, if only I was a real dog, I could have always stayed by her side."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.11,0:40:57.22,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The dog realised at the very end that this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.82,0:41:01.46,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,was love.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.22,0:41:05.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What do you think, was it interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.79,0:41:07.93,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I copied a little off The Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.80,0:41:15.79,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.21,0:41:18.74,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,liked being Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.18,0:41:24.25,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The role was a little difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.02,0:41:31.62,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,And playing it was sometimes painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.83,0:41:42.30,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,But I felt that however I was outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.96,0:41:46.87,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,whenever I came back here, I could be Momo, so I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.67,0:41:53.84,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I was happy to be held by you, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.91,0:41:57.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I liked you, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.45,0:42:08.12,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,There, there, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.83,0:42:11.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.59,0:42:13.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.70,0:42:17.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Then now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.73,0:42:20.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.20,0:42:28.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.05,0:42:33.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't have anything to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.28,0:42:41.72,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Everything I think is always read by you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.69,0:42:47.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You always see right through me, so it's kind of annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.03,0:42:56.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Even now, you can probably tell that I'm feeling really sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.11,0:43:01.41,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Even if I don't put it into words, you'd probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.89,0:43:13.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.23,0:43:20.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.93,0:43:27.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.91,0:43:33.04,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.51,0:43:37.65,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.58,0:43:41.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.50,0:43:57.97,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Hey, Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.24,0:44:01.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.54,0:44:06.04,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Can I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.74,0:44:09.78,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.42,0:44:16.25,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Because this is the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:05.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Хасуми...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.40,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Что это значит?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:09.94,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Извини, Хасуми!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:12.81,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,На следующей неделе я улетаю в Германию.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:14.98,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Желаю вам обоим счастья.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:17.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Я не шучу.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.50,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Так что...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:24.69,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Будем радоваться оставшейся неделе...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:27.16,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Хозяюшка.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.96,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Сумире-тян?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ах да, извини.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:44.41,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Надо приготовить рисовый омлет.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:50.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Хочешь заставить меня поволноваться?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Дразнишься, да?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:53.92,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Ну, Хасуми-то мы провели?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:58.65,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Да? Вот и хорошо.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.33,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Но, Момо... Ты же обещал, что навсегда останешься?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:06.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Навсегда, пока я не стану бабушкой.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.36,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Это же невозможно, если подумать.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Так не может продолжаться вечно.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:13.10,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Разве не твои слова?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:19.14,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Не знаю. Наверное, мы оба понимали...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.31,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Всё когда-нибудь закончится.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:23.04,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Верно?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Но ведь...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:34.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Нельзя же решать без меня! Осталась всего неделя!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:38.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ну, точнее, 6 дней и 2 часа.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:42.10,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Но... Понедельник, вторник, среда...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.40,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Думаю, уеду в четверг.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.77,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Надо ещё заглянуть домой и собрать вещи.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ты и правда, серьёзно?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.64,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А я тебе что твержу?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:55.24,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Конкурс-то был серьёзный.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.75,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Хотя пришлось набраться наглости, чтобы участвовать.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:01:59.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Надолго?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.08,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Почти три года.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:07.16,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Что ж, пора уже снова становиться человеком.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:28.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,И?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:33.25,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Что значит - "И"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:38.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Что, что я должна говорить после того, как ты вывалил на меня такие новости?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Не делай такое лицо.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Но, Момо!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.26,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А ты эгоистка, да, хозяюшка?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Да пройдёт неделя - и ты уже не вспомнишь Момо.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:52.63,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Забудешь обо мне и будешь тут с Хасуми.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:59.57,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Так что не надо делать такое лицо.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:02.51,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Оставила бы меня в покое? Я простая собачка.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:07.82,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Если одиноко - вокруг хватает кошек, собак, парней, которые меня заменят.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.35,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Будут послушно сидеть дома.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.72,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Можешь с ними играться и ласкать, когда пожелаешь.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Что ты несёшь? Ты серьёзно?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.06,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Момо - он не такой!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Сам знаешь, что ты не такой!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:18.73,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,А какой?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.67,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Какой я?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.54,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Кто я тебе, а, Сумире-тян?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Момо...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Момо, он...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я поняла, Момо.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:50.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Давай радоваться времени, что нам осталось.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.77,title,text,0,0,0,,МОЙ ЛЮБИМЕЦ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.77,episode,text,0,0,0,,9. В последнюю ночь
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.00,Text_1,text,0,0,0,,Осталось три дня
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Вот обещанная информация по саммиту членов ЕС.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.41,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,А, спасибо.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.75,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Так удобно систематизировано, ты меня выручила.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ну что ты.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:30.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,После введения онлайновой базы данных тут стало тише, да?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:36.03,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Но я люблю это место. Можно наугад брать что-то с полки и читать.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.00,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Кто он тебе?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.44,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Он...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:49.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}В тот момент... если бы я сказала правду...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:54.12,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Что бы он подумал обо мне?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.75,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Ну вот, опять тебя что-то беспокоит.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.13,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Ах да, а когда ты дарила букет,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.36,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,ты казалась другим человеком.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.63,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ничего подобного!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Правда, мы с ним просто дружим с детства.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:16.20,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Знаю. Я верю тебе.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:22.78,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Ладно, вечером позвоню.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:23.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Хорошо.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:37.93,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Почему я её расспрашиваю?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.30,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Вот ты где, Гото!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:46.67,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Передай своему боссу, ладно?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.07,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Ладно, окей.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.24,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,А...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.07,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,{\i1}Не уходи.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:56.01,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,{\i1}Я люблю тебя, Хасуми.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.55,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Хасуми, вам звонок на второй линии.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.45,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Хорошо.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:14.30,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Почувствуйте друг друга.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:16.97,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Так, так.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.30,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Гутен морген!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.44,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Ви гейтс?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.78,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Данке!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.28,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Зер гут!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:29.58,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Данке, данке.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.01,Petto_basic_2,Junpei,0,0,0,,А? Что вы говорите-то?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:36.38,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Я потрясён, Такеси! Ты говоришь по-немецки!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:39.69,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Я был там несколько раз. В детстве.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.69,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Стой... Что?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.26,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Гутен морген.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.70,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Ты всё-таки едешь в Германию?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.29,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Не ходи за мной, я переодеваться.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.90,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Так что это значит? Вы с ней расстались?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:52.13,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Неа. Я сказал, что уйду сам.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.87,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Ведь если бы она прогнала, мне бы захотелось умереть.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.11,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Здравствуйте.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.72,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Добрый день.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.56,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Как ваша собака, малыш Момо?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.23,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Очевидно, уезжает во Франкфурт.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.80,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Что? Франкфурт?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:21.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Да.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.13,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Он победил на престижном конкурсе.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.43,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Правда?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:31.11,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Я удивлён. Не подозревал, что вы такой выдающийся собаковод.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Нет, он сам по себе выдающийся.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:39.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Наше время вышло. Ну, до свидания.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:45.22,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Момо госпожи Иваи.. А вдруг он...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.62,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,{\i1}Может, я и мягкая, но я не домашнее животное.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:52.26,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Но желать чего-то, чего тебе не хватает - по-моему, это можно называть любовью.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:57.07,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Вдруг он мальчик с мягкой улыбкой.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.00,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,А? Мальчик?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:18.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Но тебе не кажется, что человек и любимец - намного лучше, чем один только человек?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.42,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ведь я всегда буду с тобой.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я должна проводить его правильно.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.82,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Не верю, что она смогла бы выгнать Такеси.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:57.99,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Ведь им всегда только восхищались.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:02.20,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Но я рад, что ты решил ехать. Всё-таки у тебя талант.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Вот и я.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,С возвращением!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Смотри, смотри. Ты в вечерней газете. Вот.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:13.78,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А? Уже напечатали?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ага.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:18.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Поразительно, Момо, в танце ты кажешься другим человеком.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:21.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А, наверное, не стоит называть тебя Момо.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Это...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Уважаемый Года Такеси.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,И репортёр так говорил.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.22,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я должна гордиться, что с детства дружу с Года Такеси.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Он так хотел сделать репортаж, что даже привёл с собой Хасуми - показать тебя.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.40,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.17,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Он был потрясён, сказал, никогда не видел такого высокого прыжка.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.97,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Великолепно.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:42.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Сильно и красиво. Даже я обрадовалась.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:47.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Наверное, мне не стоит хвалиться. Я ведь не имею к этому никакого отношения.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Невероятно. И такому человеку здесь не место.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.22,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Теперь я тоже буду твоей поклонницей.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.22,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Хватит.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.52,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Что за разговоры? Злят...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Почему злят?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Я же совсем не такой, правда?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:09.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Что... что ты вдруг?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.83,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Зачем - уважаемый Такеси? Ты ведь знаешь меня.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.77,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Я полный бездельник!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.71,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Я ничего не умею. Дурак, всё порчу.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Безответственный, бестолковый...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:21.51,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ты ведь сама говорила!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.88,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ты меня знаешь! Неужели ты не понимала меня?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.15,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Так зачем говоришь?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.02,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Не хочу слышать эти слова от Сумире-тян!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Зачем - не имеешь ко мне никакого отношения?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.39,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ты говорила, я бесполезный, но нужен тебе.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.86,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Я думал, одна Сумире-тян понимала...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:47.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Прости.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Всё хорошо.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Прости, всё хорошо.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.14,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Хороший мой мальчик.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Всё хорошо.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Каким бы ни был...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Где бы ни был...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:46.09,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Всегда.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я всегда буду тебя любить.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:59.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Я поняла, Момо был рядом потому же, почему и я хотела быть с ним.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:05.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Здесь мы могли стать собой.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:11.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Здесь кто-то просто принимал нас такими, какие мы есть.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Совсем скоро...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}я потеряю его навсегда.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.30,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ой, нет.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.94,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Кажется, во мне просыпается какое-то желание...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А? Что?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.00,Text_1,text,0,0,0,,Осталось два дня
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.35,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,, Эй, Сумире-тян!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.00,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Пусти вниз!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.85,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Прости! Я раскаиваюсь!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.48,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Как я могу простить озабоченного кобеля?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.42,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Но это же естественное явление!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:19.05,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Помыслы мои были чисты. Это тело как-то само...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:19.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Врёшь.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.09,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Говорю тебе, честно! Нижняя часть, она сама собой...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Молчи! Хватит с меня извинений с подробностями!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.40,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ну чего ты злишься? Я же честно.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Он ещё спрашивает! Я была в шоке!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Пригрела милую зверушку, а тут...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:38.11,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ты же не мамочка, которая нашла в комнате подростка-сына порножурналы.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А, да, есть что-то похожее.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.94,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Серьёзно?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Нет, ты ведь не продержишь меня здесь?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Не накажешь на оставшееся время?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:49.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Именно. Я не добренькая хозяйка и не избавлю от наказания только потому, что осталось два дня.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:52.99,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Стой, погоди. Что, прямо так?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.69,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Да, сегодня я, возможно, буду поздно.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.89,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Стой, стой! Стой! Эй!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:10.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Чёрт. Сколько же лет я не плакал перед кем-то?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.26,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Ивая, звонила организация из Кансая.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А, спасибо.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.36,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Хигути, не отдадите на редакцию?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:35.96,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Есть.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:38.07,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Ивая, можно вас на минутку?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Теперь проблем с построением не вижу.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А это редакторы могут выделить.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Проверьте в справочнике по стилистике.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:45.67,Petto_basic_2,Ishida,0,0,0,,Ясно.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.50,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Ивая, звонок из фотоотдела.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.65,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,Хорошо.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.45,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Ивая, по-моему, это пойдёт на статью номера.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.45,note,text,0,0,0,,Отношения человека и любимца
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Любимец?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:55.25,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Да. Помнится, у тебя собака или кто там.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:55.60,note,text,0,0,0,,Любимец
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:56.90,note,text,0,0,0,,Стресс в обществе
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.30,note,text,0,0,0,,Исцеляющая сила
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.35,note,text,0,0,0,,Любимец и человек
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.09,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Опустилась до того, что сделала из парня зверушку.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.93,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,{\i1}Мораторий не будет длиться вечно.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.73,Petto_basic_2,Fukushima,0,0,0,,{\i1}Что ты выберешь?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:04.59,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Я верю тебе.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.86,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Кто я тебе, а, Сумире-тян?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Простите!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.44,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Ивая?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Простите. Никто не виноват. Я понимаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:25.51,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Простите, мы вам перезвоним.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:29.05,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Ты... ты в порядке? Ты это... Возьми себя в руки.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:33.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А... Простите. Я...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:36.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Простите меня, в голове вдруг завертелось.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Но теперь я в порядке.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.20,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Точно?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.20,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Но на вас совсем не похоже.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:43.37,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.63,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Со мной тоже бывает.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.90,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,В ночную смену.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:50.37,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Вдруг как прорвёт: "Идиот несчастный!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.47,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,А, я тоже.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:55.48,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,Один раз пошёл в буфет, и понадкусывал все картонные стаканчики.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.68,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,Правда? Кошмар.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:00.65,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,А я раз посреди ночи швырнул на стол шефу свои ботинки.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.42,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Эй, почему я вечно злодей?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:07.56,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Ладно! Как-нибудь свожу всех, угощу.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:08.42,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Серьёзно?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.03,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Да, женщин тоже.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.53,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,И не говорите, что не останетесь после пяти.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:13.80,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Хорошо, с радостью.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.36,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Ты тоже.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Меня тоже приглашаете?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.07,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Конечно.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.60,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Нам же интересно, что там кроется за слухами.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:26.27,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Да и ты никогда не спросишь совета у вышестоящего.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А, простите.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.22,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Спасибо вам.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:42.26,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Не за что. Мы же вместе работаем, верно?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:57.64,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Нет! Я поеду только на Мальдивы.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.28,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Но я не хочу, чтобы было как у всех молодожёнов.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.00,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Наоборот!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.00,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,А если Хаконэ, как в прошлый раз?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.98,Petto_basic_2,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Нет, там мы уже были.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.82,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:08.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ой, извините. Простите.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.49,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,О нет! Нас вычислили!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:12.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.22,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Вообще-то...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:16.03,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Мы помолвлены!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:16.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Что?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.76,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Удивлены да? Наверняка.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.66,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Да уж, не ожидала.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.76,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Да я сам не ожидал.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.43,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,А, Ивая, вы тоже приходите к нам на свадьбу.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:29.10,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Но к тому времени она, может, будет уже в Рио.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я пока не планирую уезжать в Рио.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.61,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Не может быть, не едете?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.95,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Почему? Почему не едете?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:41.22,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,Эй, невежливо лезть в чужие дела.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.82,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Извините.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:46.55,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Ах, Нобу, мой милашка!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.19,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Почему? Я сама не знаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.06,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}До свидания.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Почему я совсем запуталась?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:58.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Нет смелости ни выходить замуж, ни ехать в Рио.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:01.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ни даже попросить Момо остаться...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я просто трусиха.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.86,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Откажешь ему?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Нет, попрошу подождать.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Опять ты убегаешь.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Это пока, временно.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:32.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я наконец начинаю привыкать к работе. Всё-таки я люблю её.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:36.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Тяжело, конечно, но придётся поддерживать отношения на расстоянии.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:39.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Думаю собраться с духом и сказать ему вечером.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.68,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Так, может, хотя бы распишетесь и поживёте пока раздельно?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.00,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Или хватит одной помолвки.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Но я не люблю бросать всё на полпути.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:51.99,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Но расстояние - и без обещаний?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.79,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Это же на другом конце света, да?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:55.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Да.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Здесь.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:04.30,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Что-то уж совсем далеко.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Да. Прямые рейсы всего 4 раза в неделю.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Дорога занимает, по меньшей мере, 25 часов.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:12.37,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Разница во времени 12 часов. Ему будет удобнее всего, если я буду звонить по утрам.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.44,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Уже всё подсчитала?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:15.78,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Да.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А... Момо будет тут.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.22,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Тоже неблизко...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.70,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Можно вопрос?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:41.14,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Неужели и правда не отдаёшь себе отчёта?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.94,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А? В чём?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.07,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Почему ты больше грустишь о своём пёсике?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Всё...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.08,0:20:53.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Всё совсем не так. Но он скоро уезжает.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.62,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Уверена, что это и всё?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ну конечно.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:58.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Да.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.96,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ведь он - просто любимец.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:08.10,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,В течение этого месяца я собираюсь покинуть этот дом.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.70,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Неужели?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.70,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Да.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.47,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Работа зовёт.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:25.35,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Господин Симидзу, вы были очень хорошим жильцом.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:30.59,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Вы прилежно убирали свой мусор, образцово себя вели.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:31.75,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Ну что вы.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:37.73,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Тогда сделаем так. Давайте обменяемся e-mail адресами?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.70,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Прекрасная мысль.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:44.93,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Напишите маркером на этом совке.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:47.04,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Где же маркер?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:47.60,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,А!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:51.64,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Ты! Прекрасно танцевал!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.38,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,А, вы видели?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:54.31,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Да.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:22:00.40,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Но прости. Я не помню, на каком этаже ты прописан.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.98,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,А, это потому, что я тут и не прописан.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.59,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Я был домашним животным с 4 этажа.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:09.92,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Домашним животным? Неужели у госпожи Иваи?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:10.29,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Ага.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:14.20,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Но это не значит, что господин Такеси живёт за счёт женщин.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.13,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,На следующей неделе он улетает учиться танцу во Франкфурт, в Германии.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:18.13,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Вот как.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.13,0:22:19.13,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Да.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:24.81,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Пора прощаться и с этим домом.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:37.49,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,А.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:42.32,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Если ищешь Сумире-тян, она, наверное, у Хасуми.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:43.59,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Да нет, ничего.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:46.63,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Я хотела сказать, забудь всё, что я говорила.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:50.50,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Всё-таки отказываешься от Хасуми?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:53.27,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Я лишь меняю план действий.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:55.70,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,А...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:23:02.11,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Как думаешь, если я отобью Хасуми, она станет возвращать его?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:09.42,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Нет, едва ли.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:12.32,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Да, я тоже так думаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:17.03,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Но что это значит? То есть она не любит его по-настоящему?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.66,0:23:22.36,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Думаю, любит, как простой человек.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:29.04,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Но знаешь, наверное, она не хочет показывать обиду, открывать себя настоящую.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:34.68,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,То есть клубок сплошных комплексов?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:42.70,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,И с такой-то внешностью...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:48.92,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Будь у меня её мозги, лицо и тело, я бы нашла им куда лучшее применение.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:53.70,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Но именно поэтому с ней хочется быть.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:57.77,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Ведь даже если убежишь, она не пойдёт тебя искать.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:23:59.47,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,А ты хочешь, чтобы пошла?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.27,0:24:02.17,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Хотел.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:04.84,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Хотя знал, что требую слишком много.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:08.28,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Ты слишком балуешь свою хозяйку.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:12.68,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Почему, думаешь, все больше женщин способны любить только животных?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.65,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Это, как правило, карьеристки с высоким образованием.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:17.55,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Другими словами,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:23.89,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,чтобы противостоять давлению общества, они вынуждены заковывать сердце в броню.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:25.80,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Оттого ещё больший разрыв.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.80,0:24:30.57,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Дома они хотят отбросить броню, и, не скрывая нежности, заботиться о ком-то.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:33.30,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Но они не могут раскрыться перед мужчиной.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.54,0:24:38.24,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Поэтому слишком привязываются к домашним животным.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:39.77,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Броня, говорите?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.47,0:24:42.38,Petto_basic_2,counsel,0,0,0,,Да, очень прочна, тяжёлая броня.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.84,0:24:44.99,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Знаешь, эти женщины с высшим образованием...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.99,0:24:50.79,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,У них аура так и кричит: "Не трогай меня!" Наглость какая.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.79,0:24:53.59,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Почему мужчины и ретируются.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:57.99,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,"Ах так? Ну и пожалуйста, живи как знаешь!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.99,0:24:59.66,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Так и отвечают.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:03.83,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Понятно, буду жить как знаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.70,0:25:05.83,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Что? Почему?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.83,0:25:08.77,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Видимо, я последовательница Иваи.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.14,0:25:13.61,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Но в резюме ты написала...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.61,0:25:17.61,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Я солгала. Я учусь на 4 курсе филологического факультета Токийского университета.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.61,0:25:23.59,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Ведь окажись я умной женщиной, вы бы не наняли меня, верно, доктор?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.92,0:25:27.66,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Верно.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:34.50,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Если подумать, а ты ещё никогда не оставалась у меня, да, Ивая?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.96,0:25:38.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А, и правда.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.07,0:25:44.21,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,В прошлый раз ты сразу убежала домой, сказав, что должна покормить собаку.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.04,0:25:51.91,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Ну, о чём хотела поговорить?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.78,0:25:58.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А... Ни о чём.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.62,0:26:00.46,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Это не так важно.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.60,0:26:10.97,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Знаешь, сегодня шеф вызвал меня к себе.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.90,0:26:14.94,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Решено, я возвращаюсь в Рио в следующем месяце.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.24,0:26:22.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Вот как?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.31,0:26:28.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Всё решено?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.56,0:26:39.86,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Ты останешься сегодня?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.10,0:26:41.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А? Но...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.63,0:26:43.37,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Почему нет?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.37,0:26:50.74,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Ты меня беспокоишь. И кольцо ни разу не надевала.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.04,0:26:54.78,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я просто боялась его поцарапать.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.78,0:26:58.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,И не хотелось, чтобы на работе болтали.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.35,0:27:00.82,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Знаешь, дело не в том, что я не хочу выходить замуж.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.82,0:27:05.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Но у меня есть работа, и я ещё не разобралась в своих чувствах.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.79,0:27:07.96,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Правда, что всё дело в этом?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.89,0:27:17.43,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Честно говоря, я понятия не имею, о чём ты думаешь.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.14,0:27:23.41,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Хотя бы передо мной, покажи настоящую себя.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.68,0:27:29.41,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Настоящую себя?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.21,0:27:32.91,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Настоящую Иваю, какая она есть.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.49,0:27:39.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А что значит "какая есть"?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.79,0:27:42.66,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Какое лицо я должна показать?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.92,0:27:45.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Какая я в твоём представлении?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.03,0:27:49.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я просто...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.66,0:27:54.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Хотела, чтобы ты меня любил, хотела стать той, какой ты меня видишь.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.10,0:27:56.57,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я даже не могу показать тебе своих чувств.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.57,0:27:59.57,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я не знаю, какую часть меня ты видишь.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.57,0:28:02.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Не так просто показать настоящую себя.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.78,0:28:07.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Настоящая я...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.82,0:28:10.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Намного хуже.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.02,0:28:16.89,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Хуже.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.26,0:28:21.19,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Ивая...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.00,0:28:21.70,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,Тот мальчик...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.00,0:28:28.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Мальчик, которому я подарила букет, он не мой друг детства.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.11,0:28:32.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Он мой...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.68,0:28:39.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Мой любимец.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.38,0:28:46.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я держала его дома вместо собаки.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.35,0:28:47.42,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Любимец?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.23,0:28:54.16,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Тогда Момо...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.66,0:28:56.53,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Прости, я солгала тебе.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.53,0:28:58.93,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Но я не хотела, чтобы ты неправильно понял.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.27,0:29:02.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Между нами ничего нет, просто хорошие отношения.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.74,0:29:04.91,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Хорошие отношения?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.51,0:29:08.24,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Ты всерьёз это говоришь?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.62,0:29:20.29,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Что...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.56,0:29:22.92,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Прошу, уходи.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.16,0:29:26.26,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Пожалуйста.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.10,0:29:29.90,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Я должен подумать. Один.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.40,0:29:36.74,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Уходи, пожалуйста!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.61,0:29:41.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Прости.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.92,0:29:51.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Успокойся.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.02,0:29:52.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Давай успокойся.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.90,0:30:03.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А, Сумире-тян. С возвращением.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.03,0:30:05.00,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ай!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.57,0:30:06.23,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.54,0:30:11.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Вот и всё.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.44,0:30:20.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Всё кончено.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.79,0:30:30.89,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Всё-таки рассказала?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.63,0:30:34.36,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Сколько я врал ради тебя, а ты всё испортила.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.20,0:30:39.27,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Гадство.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.84,0:30:50.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Сейчас приготовлю.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.92,0:30:55.48,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Да ничего уж.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.05,0:31:00.52,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Я не против, если мы так останемся все два дня.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.36,0:31:06.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Потому что только передо мной Сумире-тян может плакать.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.60,0:31:20.11,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Людям нужен кто-то, с кем они могут быть эгоистичными.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.24,0:31:23.45,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Поэтому...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.61,0:31:28.62,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Поэтому я был привязан к этому дому.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.30,0:31:59.30,Text_1,text,0,0,0,,Остался один день
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.45,0:32:04.62,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,А где Ивая?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.62,0:32:07.09,Petto_basic,Nobu,0,0,0,,Похоже, взяла отгул на сегодня и завтра.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.66,0:32:10.23,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Наверное, она и правда себя плохо чувствует.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.13,0:32:13.03,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Босс?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.03,0:32:13.70,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Чего?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.70,0:32:15.03,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Это вам.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.80,0:32:17.00,note,text,0,0,0,,Заявление об уходе
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.07,0:32:17.77,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,А?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.77,0:32:19.90,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Примите, пожалуйста.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.67,0:32:26.98,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Всё, готово!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.48,0:32:31.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Вот! Пожелания на сегодняшнее и завтрашнее меню.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:35.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Не многовато ли углеводов?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.15,0:32:36.79,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Какая разница?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.29,0:32:39.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ну хорошо, сделаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.69,0:32:40.79,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ура!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.73,0:32:44.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Кто там?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.16,0:32:46.96,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Вот ваше расписание.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.20,0:32:48.33,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Расписание составил?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.33,0:32:50.77,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Да, завтра утром я заезжаю за вами.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.77,0:32:52.97,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Прошу, подготовьте к тому времени вещи.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.57,0:32:53.74,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Не надо за мной заезжать.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.74,0:32:55.37,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Я и сам доберусь до дома.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.37,0:32:57.87,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Нет, а вдруг по дороге с вами что случится.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.87,0:32:58.54,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Не случится.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.54,0:33:01.28,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Нет, вы иногда очень рассеянны, осторожность не помешает.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.28,0:33:04.71,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Итак, мы отвезём вас прямо домой в Тибу, будем допаковывать вещи.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.71,0:33:09.72,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,А три дня спустя, 14 июня в 13:00, вы вылетаете из аэропорта Нарита.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.82,0:33:09.85,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Слушай...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.95,0:33:10.99,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Да?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.99,0:33:12.85,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Займись-ка снова балетом.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.19,0:33:17.13,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,По-моему, тебе это больше подходит.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.56,0:33:20.66,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Да, я подумаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.66,0:33:21.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Извините...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.06,0:33:24.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Сделать вам чаю?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.87,0:33:28.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Кто там?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.90,0:33:31.37,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Вот те на, господин Симидзу, и вы тут?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.37,0:33:32.44,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Да, чуть опередил вас.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.44,0:33:37.41,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Такеси, вот тебе глобус. Он может там пригодиться.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.41,0:33:38.41,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Спасибо.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.88,0:33:41.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Так, что, всем сделать чаю?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.85,0:33:43.85,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А теперь кто?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.22,0:33:46.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Что?! Как здесь образовалось это сборище?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.49,0:33:47.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Сама не понимаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.02,0:33:49.52,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А, сестричка.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.52,0:33:51.69,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Давненько не виделись, братишка.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.86,0:33:52.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А ты, Юри?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.99,0:33:54.00,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Что, я?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.46,0:33:57.17,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Заскочила глянуть на него в последний раз.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.80,0:34:00.87,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Смотрю, у вас веселее, чем я ожидала.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.94,0:34:02.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Юри...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.87,0:34:05.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Знаешь, а Хасуми...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.24,0:34:08.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я сказала ему правду.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:10.05,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,А?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.31,0:34:12.98,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,То есть - о пёсике?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.50,0:34:14.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Угу.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.89,0:34:19.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Так и знала!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.49,0:34:20.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Что ты хочешь сказать - знала?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.79,0:34:24.09,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,А знала, что не сможешь долго скрывать от него любимчика.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.33,0:34:25.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А? Почему это?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.03,0:34:29.86,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Потому что он стал слишком важным, чтобы его можно было и дальше прятать.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.17,0:34:34.24,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Да Хасуми, думаю, и сам в глубине души знал, что ты что-то скрываешь.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.67,0:34:38.97,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Какое-то время я думала, ты всё-таки выберешь его...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.87,0:34:40.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,То есть?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.98,0:34:42.18,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,А что?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.18,0:34:47.48,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Помнишь брачную клятву? Цитирую: "В болезни и во здравии..."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.48,0:34:50.62,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,В этом мире не много таких людей.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.99,0:34:55.49,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Больная или здоровая, когда подавлена и хочется плакать...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.49,0:34:56.76,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Даже на необитаемом острове.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.76,0:34:59.79,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Даже без косметики. Тот, кто необходим тебе, куда бы ни отправилась.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.83,0:35:02.60,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Вот в чем особенность.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.73,0:35:08.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Но он уезжает.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.21,0:35:16.75,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Так, ребята. Ну-ка, собираемся.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.75,0:35:20.62,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Но мы едим... О, мне пора на обход!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.52,0:35:21.85,Petto_basic_2,Yuri,0,0,0,,Вот видишь?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.95,0:35:23.92,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Я должен спешить. Благодарю за угощение.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.19,0:35:27.36,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Ну, оставляем вас. Хорошо провести время!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:28.59,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Значит, до завтра...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.06,0:35:30.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Пока, спасибо!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.11,0:35:46.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,И... что будем делать?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.24,0:35:49.74,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,М-м-м... Ну...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.31,0:35:53.45,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А если... ванну?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.48,0:36:23.48,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Балдёж!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.22,0:36:29.32,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Ай! Горячо!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.32,0:36:31.99,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ничего не горячо, сиди смирно.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.99,0:36:39.33,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Всё! Чисто!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.59,0:36:41.63,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Ах ты, как в раю.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.50,0:36:44.87,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Я сегодня чувствую себя прямо принцем.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.67,0:36:50.77,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Алло?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.17,0:36:51.17,Petto_basic_ending_2,counsel,0,0,0,,Алло?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.51,0:36:53.98,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Это ваш товарищ!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.04,0:36:56.98,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,А, здравствуйте.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.31,0:37:00.18,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Знаете, я всё думал...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.18,0:37:06.32,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Что вечная любовь - это всего лишь компромисс.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.32,0:37:10.79,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Любовь - это нечто низменное, в чём люди соперничают и обманывают.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.79,0:37:13.53,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,И упиваются притворством, что якобы заботятся друг о друге.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.53,0:37:16.90,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,А стоит влюбиться - и ты проиграл.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.90,0:37:17.87,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Понятно.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.87,0:37:22.00,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,И невозможно просто так любить человека, как любят собаку.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.00,0:37:25.91,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Без расчёта, без мыслей о качествах и образовании другого.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.21,0:37:27.21,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Но...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.38,0:37:32.01,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Но думаю, сейчас я выздоровел.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.01,0:37:32.75,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Что?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.35,0:37:35.65,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Да, передавайте привет Момо!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.18,0:37:38.49,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Скажите, я хотел бы когда-нибудь познакомиться с ним.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.89,0:37:45.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,С работы?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.53,0:37:47.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Нет, психотерапевт.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.83,0:37:49.40,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Передавал тебе привет.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.40,0:37:54.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Он хороший человек. Всегда носит с собой чихуахуа.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.64,0:37:57.44,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Похоже, занятная личность.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.74,0:38:02.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ну... а теперь? Ещё пожелания на сегодня?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.68,0:38:04.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Что теперь...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.91,0:38:07.28,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А если массаж ног?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.28,0:38:07.85,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Конечно.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.02,0:38:11.02,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Щекотно!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.02,0:38:11.86,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ты чего?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.86,0:38:13.50,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Давай лучше я тебе сделаю.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.56,0:38:16.12,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Не, не надо. Я тоже боюсь щекотки.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.53,0:38:20.46,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Да...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.53,0:38:22.33,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Да...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.27,0:38:31.41,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Чего?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.51,0:38:35.71,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Если скоро не решим, ночь кончится.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.21,0:38:41.38,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А давай тогда рассказывать истории?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.38,0:38:42.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Истории?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.35,0:38:44.02,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ага, истории о любви.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.19,0:38:47.26,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Там, "Первая любовь?" или "Когда лишилась девственности?"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.26,0:38:48.09,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Типа того.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.09,0:38:49.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я не стану об этом рассказывать.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.56,0:38:51.03,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Тогда я первый.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.10,0:38:56.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ну ладно, первая любовь?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.20,0:38:58.57,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Дай подумать.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.83,0:39:04.67,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Давным-давно, в одном королевстве жила Принцесса Которая Не Плакала.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.27,0:39:06.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Принцесса?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.50,0:39:07.50,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Да.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.51,0:39:12.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Принцесса Которая Не Плакала была ну очень красивая, серьёзная.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.61,0:39:17.89,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А ещё умная. Но она не очень умела выражать свои чувства
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.89,0:39:20.42,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,и потому жила в замке в одиночестве.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.56,0:39:23.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Сказка, случайно, не про меня?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.83,0:39:26.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Слушай дальше. Хорошее только начинается.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.06,0:39:32.37,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Однажды Принцессу оставил мужчина.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.37,0:39:34.90,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А она нашла картонную коробку, внутри которой свернулся Пёс.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.97,0:39:38.74,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,На самом-то деле Пёс был человеком,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.74,0:39:41.78,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,но он был так счастлив, что его спасла Принцесса,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.01,0:39:46.21,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,что стал собакой и поселился у неё.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.75,0:39:49.12,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Вообще-то, он собирался сразу же уйти домой.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.25,0:39:52.69,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Но сам не заметил, как очень полюбил замок.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.29,0:39:57.56,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Почему? Потому что Принцесса Которая Не Плакала
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.43,0:40:02.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,могла ронять свои прекрасные слёзы только перед ним.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.00,0:40:12.57,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Но тут перед Принцессой появился Прекрасный Принц.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.51,0:40:20.75,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Конечно, то был удар для Пса, но пока он оставался животным, принцесса ценила его.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.75,0:40:23.69,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Он решил ещё немного побыть собакой.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.25,0:40:25.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Момо...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.79,0:40:32.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,И вот Принц предложил Принцессе руку и сердце.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.30,0:40:37.07,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Пёс решил вернуться домой.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.73,0:40:39.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Момо, не надо больше.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.34,0:40:41.97,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Пёс подумал:
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.67,0:40:50.75,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,"Эх, был бы я настоящей собакой - мог бы навсегда остаться рядом с ней".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.11,0:40:57.22,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,В самом конце, Пёс понял, что это было.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.82,0:41:01.46,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Это была любовь.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.22,0:41:05.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ну, как, интересно вышло?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.79,0:41:07.93,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Правда, кое-что пришлось стащить из "Русалочки".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.80,0:41:15.79,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Мне...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.21,0:41:18.74,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,нравилось быть Момо.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.18,0:41:24.25,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Роль чуточку непростая.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.02,0:41:31.62,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,И иногда было больно играть.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.83,0:41:42.30,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Но я чувствовал, каким бы я ни был во внешнем мире,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.96,0:41:46.87,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,когда возвращался сюда, я мог стать Момо, и был счастлив.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.67,0:41:53.84,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Сумире-тян, я был рад, что ты заботилась обо мне.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.91,0:41:57.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Сумире-тян, я любил тебя.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.45,0:42:08.12,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ну, не плачь.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.83,0:42:11.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Держи.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.59,0:42:13.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Я не плачу.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.70,0:42:17.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,А теперь твоя очередь.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.73,0:42:20.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Моя?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.20,0:42:28.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,А я...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.05,0:42:33.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Мне нечего сказать.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.28,0:42:41.72,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Момо всё равно читает каждую мою мысль.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.69,0:42:47.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ты всегда видишь меня насквозь. Даже злит.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.03,0:42:56.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,И сейчас ты, наверное, знаешь, что мне очень грустно.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.11,0:43:01.41,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Даже если я ничего не скажу, ты...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.89,0:43:13.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Не надо...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.23,0:43:20.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Останься.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.93,0:43:27.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Не уезжай.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.91,0:43:33.04,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Не уезжай никуда.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.51,0:43:37.65,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Сумире-тян?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.58,0:43:41.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Не оставляй меня.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.50,0:43:57.97,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Скажи, Сумире-тян?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.24,0:44:01.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Чего?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.54,0:44:06.04,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Можно тебя поцеловать?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.74,0:44:09.78,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Ведь...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.42,0:44:16.25,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Ведь это последний раз...